text.text:
Mānawa Bay has been designed to set a new benchmark for outlet shopping in New Zealand. Mānawa Bay will be a purpose-built destination focused on delivering a customer-led experience bringing the best fashion, athleisure, lifestyle and homeware brands together under one roof. Nestled on the water’s edge overlooking the mangroves, Mānawa Bay will offer great shopping, unique park-like grounds and outdoor spaces within our estuary location.

 

A unique opportunity, leasing now.

text_copy.text: Mānawa Bay will be easily accessible being close to Auckland Airport, motorways and main arterial routes.

text_copy_copy.text:
Mānawa Bay will accommodate a wide range 

of transport modes, including public and future 

mass transit. Designed to welcome everyone, we will offer ample parking, an intuitive retail layout and quality facilities, with a unique food and beverage offering including beautiful indoor and outdoor dining spaces.
Be part of Mānawa Bay, New Zealand’s leading premium outlet shopping destination.

text_copy_copy_copy.text: A sought after premium proposition, designed to set a new benchmark for outlet shopping in New Zealand. Mānawa Bay will be a purpose-built destination focussed on delivering a customer-centric experience bringing the best fashion, athleisure, lifestyle and homeware brands together under one roof. Home to a curated food and beverage offering, customers can dine in the relaxed light-filled indoor setting or our alfresco outdoor space overlooking the water.

text_copy_copy.text:
Mānawa Bay will be easily accessible for Aucklanders and those visiting from out of town.Conveniently located close to the airport, motorways and main arterial routes, only a 25-minute drive from Auckland CBD, accommodating all forms of transport, including public and future mass transit.Approximately 90% of the city’s population, 1.6 million people, live within a 30 minute drive of Mānawa Bay.

 

**Macroplan Auckland Airport market potential for outlet retail, April 2021

text_copy_copy.text: A substantial market with untapped potential and significant expected growth.

text_copy_copy_copy.text: Mānawa Bay has been positively received with strong appeal and high visitation intent from both Auckland and wider New Zealand.*
